1
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:04,200
I made some porridge.

2
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:06,760
That's great!

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:09,640
Eat up, so you can get better soon.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,560
Hinata...

5
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:16,040
Feed me.

6
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:24,160
This is delicious.

7
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:26,600
It's just a pre-made pack.

8
00:00:26,720 --> 00:00:28,000
No.

9
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,360
I'm so lucky to have such a sweet little brother.

10
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,800
That's hot!

11
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,240
Hey!

12
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,480
Alright, just get some sleep.

13
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:39,680
Want to sleep together?

14
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,720
I'll catch your cold.
Spare me, please.

15
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:56,240
I'm sorry I shouldn't have yelled at you.

16
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:00,000
You scared me to death.

17
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,520
You were so loud all of a sudden.

18
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,160
I was just worried about you.

19
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:08,040
I was afraid something might happen to you.

20
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:11,000
You're such a weirdo.

21
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,680
Anyway, just get some sleep.

22
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,600
Whoa!
